The proof of Anderson localization then follows from a similar argument as in the proof of Lemma <a href="#lem:I1_small" data-reference-type="ref" data-reference="lem:I1_small">42</a>. Indeed, similarly to <a href="#eq:phi0" data-reference-type="eqref" data-reference="eq:phi0">[eq:phi0]</a>, one has $$\begin{aligned}
