\end{aligned}$$ By the convexity of $L^2_{\varepsilon}(\omega,M_{E,AA}^{HH^*})$ in $\varepsilon\in (\varepsilon_1,\infty)$, we have, $$\begin{aligned}
\label{eq:lb_L^2_AA_3}
    L^2_{\varepsilon=0}(\omega,M_{E,AA}^{HH^*})\geq 2\log |\lambda_3/\lambda_2|\geq 2\log |\lambda|+O(1).
\end{aligned}$$ Simple estimates on the sup norm of $M_{E,AA}^{HH^*}$ show $$\begin{aligned}
\label{eq:ub_L^1_AA}
